|人物 = {{ill|Kose Otoko|de|Kose Otoko|ja|巨勢男人|lt=Man|lt_ja=男人|lt_de=Man|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Otoko|qq=}}<br/>{{ill|Kose Hirao|de|Kose Hirao|ja|巨勢比良夫|lt=Hirao|lt_ja=比良夫|lt_de=Hirao|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Hirao|qq=}}<br/>{{ill|Kose Tokuda|de|Kose Tokuda|ja|巨勢徳陀|lt=Tokuda|lt_ja=徳陀|lt_de=Tokuda|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Tokuda|qq=}}<br/>{{ill|Kose Hito|de|Kose Hito|ja|巨勢人|lt=Hito|lt_ja=人|lt_de=Hito|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Hito|qq=}}<br/>{{ill|Kose Neta Maro|de|Kose Neta Maro|ja|巨勢奈弖麻呂|lt=Neta Maro|lt_ja=奈弖麻呂|lt_de=Neta Maro|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Neta Maro|qq=}}<br/>{{ill|Kose Noashi|de|Kose Noashi|ja|巨勢野足|lt=Noashi|lt_ja=野足|lt_de=Noashi|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kose Noashi|qq=}}<br/>[[:en:Kose Kanaoka|Kanaoka]]<br/>{{ill|Jōen-in|de|Jōen-in|ja|浄円院|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jōen-in|qq=}} ?
